      "id": "file:code/b2_run_skill.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "b2_run_skill.py",
      "filePath": "code/b2_run_skill.py",
      "summary": "Skill独立运行的入口模块，通过动态导入（importlib）执行指定Skill函数，捕获异常并生成标准化SkillResult，支持CLI参数解析和JSONL运行日志记录。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "skill-executor", "cli", "dynamic-import"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 importlib.import_module 和 inspect.signature 实现反射式动态函数调用，根据函数签名自动注入 data_root 和 output_dir 参数。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:code/b3_tool_layer.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "b3_tool_layer.py",
      "filePath": "code/b3_tool_layer.py",
      "summary": "工具层核心模块，从YAML配置加载工具定义、生成符合OpenAI风格的function-calling JSON Schema、校验工具调用参数类型，并通过动态导入执行具体Skill函数，是整个Agent工具调用链路的枢纽。",
      "tags": ["tool-layer", "schema-generation", "validation", "cli", "api-handler"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "生成与OpenAI function-calling兼容的JSON Schema（含 x-returns 扩展字段），支持integer/number类型严格校验（排除bool误判），根据函数签名自动注入 data_root 和 output_dir。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:code/b4_local_agent_llm.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "b4_local_agent_llm.py",
      "filePath": "code/b4_local_agent_llm.py",
      "summary": "本地LLM推理引擎模块，支持mock模式和真实transformers推理两种后端，负责构建含工具schema和格式指令的prompt messages、解析模型原始输出为标准化AIMessage，并缓存已加载的模型/分词器实例以减少重复加载开销。",
      "tags": ["llm-inference", "prompt-engineering", "model-cache", "json-parsing", "cli"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "实现多级JSON解析容错策略（标准解析→尾随反引号截断→tool_calls片段提取），模型缓存在模块级字典中使用可哈希元组键避免重复加载，支持bfloat16/float16/float32 dtype配置。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:code/common/path_utils.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "path_utils.py",
      "filePath": "code/common/path_utils.py",
